&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">说明 地址 原始值 修改为
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Initial License Check 0x003A31F2 55 41 57 41 48 31 C0 C3
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Persistent License Check 1 0x00399387 E8 08 0E 12 00 90 90 90 90 90
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Persistent License Check 2 0x0039939D E8 F2 0D 12 00 90 90 90 90 90
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Disable Server Validation Thread 0x003A4E30 55 41 56 53 41 89 F6 48 31 C0 48 FF C0 C3
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Disable License Notify Thread 0x003A2E82 41 C3
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Disable Crash Reporter 0x0038C9F0 55 C3
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>修改完成后，另存为，替换掉/opt/sublime_text/sublime_text，添加+x 权限，否则不能运行&lt;/p>
